profile: Family owned and operated furniture and mattress retailer since 1926 in Campbellford, Peterborough and now Kingston. A destination store with the largest selection of solid wood furniture, custom upholstery including La-Z-Boy, and complimentary design services available. Delivers up to 100km from any store location from west of Toronto all the way to Ottawa, and cottage country!
